            <title><![CDATA[What share of people say they are vegetarian, vegan, or flexitarian?]]></title>
            <id>https://ourworldindata.org/vegetarian-vegan</id>
            <link rel="alternate" href="https://ourworldindata.org/vegetarian-vegan"/>
            <published>2022-05-13T09:00:00.000Z</published>
            <updated>2022-05-16T20:44:04.000Z</updated>
            <author><name>Edouard Mathieu</name></author><author><name>Hannah Ritchie</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[Most people still eat some meat. But survey data shows that many report adopting a diet with less animal products. Young people are more likely to be non- or only occasional meat-eaters.<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/vegetarian-vegan" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2022/05/British-diets-thumbnail-768x301.png"/></a>]]></summary>
            </entry>
